<br>
This understanding is based on living with an enforcer that uses the sheilds,  if she gets hit by X damage type through a fight she'll renew the sheild because it's abative effects for the damage type are gone, but it still has abative effects for other damage types, so the sheild is still &quot;up&quot; just not for that specific damage type.<br>
<br>
By using 3 kinds of damage, if this understanding is correct, you'd only make the shield more effective at protecting from your damage.<br>
<br>
